@startuml A2_04_component_enrollment_service_simple
title Enrollment Service – Simplified View

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #000000
  BorderThickness 1
}

rectangle "Enrollment Service\nPort: 8090" as ENROLLMENT_SERVICE {
  rectangle "API Layer\n(6 endpoints)" as API_LAYER
  rectangle "Engines\n(degree audit, scenarios,\nschedule, transfer, budget)" as ENGINES
  rectangle "Data Repositories\n(enrollment, financial, graph)" as REPOS
}

database "Postgres\n(Enrollment + Financial)" as PG_DB
database "Neo4j\n(Knowledge Graph)" as NEO4J
cloud "RAG Service" as RAG
cloud "Observability" as OBS

API_LAYER --> ENGINES
ENGINES --> REPOS
REPOS --> PG_DB : enrollment, financial data
REPOS --> NEO4J : prerequisites, requirements
ENGINES --> RAG : policy context
ENROLLMENT_SERVICE --> OBS

note right of ENROLLMENT_SERVICE
**Role:** Enrollment Engine
**Tech:** FastAPI
**Key Functions:**
- Degree audits
- Scenario comparisons
- Schedule optimization
- Transfer equivalency
- Budget calculation
end note

@enduml

